name: SIHI Pump ZTND 100250 AA 002 1B 2G7
description:
Horizontal, single-stage volute pump with
dimensions and nominal ratings to DIN 24255/
EN 733 in back pull-out design. This series
has especially been designed for handling
heat transfer oils up to 350 °C



10141352 bare shaft

shaft sealing: Radial seal rings

Gewicht ca. 90kg
